    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，与加拿大墨西哥的贸易紧张关系对世界杯有益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-says-trade-tension-with-mexico-canada-good-for-world-cup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他与墨西哥和加拿大的贸易纠纷对2026年与这两个国家共同主持的世界杯有益，因为他签署了一项行政命令，以建立一个工作队来协助组织比赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-says-trade-tension-with-mexico-canada-good-for-world-cup</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 20:17:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Oreo-Maker Mondelez转向新的SEC指导，以安静地要求俄罗斯透明度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/mondelez-is-looking-to-discard-a-shareholder-resolution-on-its-russia-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙德勒斯国际公司（Mondelez International Inc.）要求监管机构允许忽略股东提案，该提议要求对奥利奥（Oreo）制造商的俄罗斯业务提高透明度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/mondelez-is-looking-to-discard-a-shareholder-resolution-on-its-russia-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 19:49:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队权衡结束油价上限，如果俄罗斯谈论进度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-team-weighs-ending-oil-price-cap-if-russia-talks-progress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的顾问正在勾勒出他可以提出或调整的潜在制裁措施。包括油价上限＆Mdash;据熟悉此事的人们说，如果与莫斯科结束在乌克兰的战争方面取得了进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-team-weighs-ending-oil-price-cap-if-russia-talks-progress</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 19:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的批准在民意调查中跳来跳去，因为法国担心乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/macron-s-approval-jumps-in-poll-as-french-worry-about-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据Ifop for Ouest-France的一项民意调查，伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）的批准率提高到自6月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/macron-s-approval-jumps-in-poll-as-french-worry-about-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 19:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国准备命令更多公司停止在委内瑞拉开业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-poised-to-order-more-companies-to-stop-operating-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，特朗普政府正准备迫使更多公司停止在委内瑞拉工作，并在命令雪佛龙公司命令尼古拉斯·马杜罗（Nicolas Maduro）的总统压力下，以结束在那里的运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-poised-to-order-more-companies-to-stop-operating-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 19:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国议员受到马斯克的称赞，被改革主席指控威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/uk-lawmaker-praised-by-musk-accused-of-threats-by-reform-chair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国改革英国表示，这位由埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）吹捧的议员可能是领导人奈杰尔·法拉奇（Nigel Farage）两次威胁该党主席，并且还在调查其办公室中欺凌的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/uk-lawmaker-praised-by-musk-accused-of-threats-by-reform-chair</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 18:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大承诺数十亿美元，以帮助贸易动荡伤害的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/canada-rolls-out-4-5-billion-program-to-aid-tariff-hit-firms-m7z2uuqe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多（Justin Trudeau）的政府分配了65亿加元（45亿美元），以帮助出口商到达加拿大产品的新市场，因为该国的商业部门向唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争提供服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/canada-rolls-out-4-5-billion-program-to-aid-tariff-hit-firms-m7z2uuqe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普以4亿美元的联邦赠款削减了反犹太主义的奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-hits-columbia-with-400-million-in-cuts-over-antisemitism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府表示，将取消4亿美元的联邦赠款和哥伦比亚大学的合同，理由是犹太学生对常春藤联盟学校的民权投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-hits-columbia-with-400-million-in-cuts-over-antisemitism</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:50:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他可能会与乳制品，木材关税达成加拿大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-says-he-may-hit-canada-with-dairy-lumber-tariffs-shortly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他可能会在星期五立即对加拿大木材和乳制品产品实施互惠关税，威胁要再次破坏与美国主要合作伙伴的贸易，并重新激发长期以来一直是跨境纠纷中心的两家行业的斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-says-he-may-hit-canada-with-dairy-lumber-tariffs-shortly</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
